    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips when shifting into third gear; additionally, the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a non-functional AC system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it is recommended that the buyer tows it away.",
      "price": 6500.0,
